text:
$XFAB is increasingly being reframed from a legacy European foundry into a photonics and power-semiconductor infrastructure play.

@aleabitoreddit argues the market may still be underpricing X-FAB’s exposure to silicon photonics, SiC and AI power-semiconductor manufacturing.

The broader theme is that the AI infrastructure trade is now expanding deeper into older foundry capacity, photonics manufacturing and 800V power ecosystems.

